Cleared for Disaster



Aired on 03/22/2010, Narrated by Jonathan Aris



On 1 February 1991, USAir Flight 1493, a Boeing 737-300, inbound for landing, collides with SkyWest Airlines Flight 5569, a Fairchild Metro III, sitting on the runway, awaiting takeoff clearance, killing 34 people.
